<collectionCode box="[347,400,1945,1971]" pageId="11" pageNumber="60">TIII</collectionCode>
), and bases of tarsus I and tarsus II yellow; basal half of dorsal surface of FI slightly infuscate. Anterior surface of CxI covered by pale setae, distal half and outer edge with brownish setae; anterior surface of CxII with 
<number box="[528,544,152,178]" pageId="12" pageNumber="61" value="1.0">1</number>
